## 🔄 Rate Limiting & Retries

This server implements intelligent retry logic:

- **Automatic Retries:** Failed requests are retried up to `MAX_RETRIES` times
- **Exponential Backoff:** Wait time increases between retries (1s, 2s, 4s, etc.)
- **Smart Retry Logic:**
  - ✅ **Retries:** Network errors, 500/502/503/504 server errors
  - ❌ **No Retry:** 400/401/403/404 client errors, validation failures

**Rate Limit Handling:**
- 429 errors trigger exponential backoff
- The server logs retry attempts for debugging
- Check logs with `LOG_LEVEL=debug` to see retry behavior

